7
00:01:32,677 --> 00:01:34,004
<font color="yellow">Yeon Hui.</font>

8
00:01:38,188 --> 00:01:40,484
<font color="yellow">Rahib Yoh Gwang.</font>

9
00:01:40,484 --> 00:01:43,358
<font color="yellow"><i>[Episode 10]</i></font>

10
00:01:46,501 --> 00:01:47,998
<font color="yellow">Ada apa?</font>

11
00:01:50,618 --> 00:01:53,808
<font color="yellow">Kakakmu tahu masalah ini?</font>

12
00:01:53,808 --> 00:01:57,655
<font color="yellow">- Dia pasti tak tahu.
- Kenapa?</font>

13
00:01:57,655 --> 00:02:01,251
<font color="yellow">- Ayo beritahukan semua padanya--
- Aku bisa bilang apa?</font>

14
00:02:01,251 --> 00:02:04,960
<font color="yellow">Haruskah kubilang aku berubah jadi penyihir jahat akibat kutukan?</font>

15
00:02:04,960 --> 00:02:08,033
<font color="yellow">Atau dia sebaiknya lari dariku karena mungkin bisa mati jika tak lari?</font>

16
00:02:08,033 --> 00:02:10,942
<font color="yellow">Tak ada yang pernah memberitahukannya padaku.</font>

17
00:02:10,942 --> 00:02:14,675
<font color="yellow">Bahkan aku tak tahu kenapa terlahir dengan kutukan ini.</font>

18
00:02:16,151 --> 00:02:18,330
<font color="yellow">Aku bisa bilang apa padanya?</font>

19
00:02:23,103 --> 00:02:25,546
<font color="yellow">Aku tak bisa apa-apa kalau kau tak ingin cerita padanya.</font>

20
00:02:25,546 --> 00:02:28,884
<font color="yellow">Tapi kakakmu pasti ingin dengar penjelasan darimu.</font>

21
00:02:30,384 --> 00:02:34,070
<font color="yellow">Kupikir kau tak lagi sembunyi dan melarikan diri.</font>

22
00:02:37,858 --> 00:02:40,774
<font color="yellow"><i>[Aku ingin temui lagi dia yang kurindukan.]</i>
<i>- Syukurlah</i></font>

23
00:02:40,774 --> 00:02:44,513
<font color="yellow">kau dan Yeon Hui selamat dan baik-baik saja.</font>

24
00:02:44,513 --> 00:02:49,331
<font color="yellow">Kau pasti mengkhawatirkan kami. Kami tak bisa menghubungimu karena suatu alasan.</font>

25
00:02:49,331 --> 00:02:53,626
<font color="yellow">Apa Yeon Hui menghindariku karena alasan itu?</font>

26
00:02:53,626 --> 00:02:56,801
<font color="yellow">Jadi bukan karena tak bisa temukan aku</font>

27
00:02:56,801 --> 00:02:59,418
<font color="yellow">tapi karena lari dariku?</font>

28
00:02:59,418 --> 00:03:02,926
<font color="yellow">Kau pasti frustrasi. Ada sebab kenapa tak bisa kami ceritakan.</font>

29
00:03:02,926 --> 00:03:07,706
<font color="yellow">Dengan mengabaikannya, Yeon Hui dan aku sudah terbantu.</font>

30
00:03:07,706 --> 00:03:10,670
<font color="yellow">Itulah yang kudengar dari Ayah sejak masih muda.</font>

31
00:03:10,670 --> 00:03:14,233
<font color="yellow">"Jangan bertemu dengan Yeon Hui. Jangan tanya kenapa."</font>

32
00:03:15,408 --> 00:03:17,912
<font color="yellow">Apakah sebaiknya kutemui Yeon Hui atau tidak</font>

33
00:03:17,912 --> 00:03:21,144
<font color="yellow">dan apakah sebaiknya kutahu kenapa jangan dan sebaiknya...</font>

34
00:03:21,144 --> 00:03:23,323
<font color="yellow">aku memutuskannya.</font>

35
00:03:42,098 --> 00:03:44,427
<font color="yellow">Terima kasih masih tetap hidup.</font>

36
00:04:24,887 --> 00:04:26,637
<font color="yellow">Bawa lari semua orang!</font>

37
00:04:35,399 --> 00:04:38,620
<font color="yellow">Setelah mendengar ada angkatan bersenjata di Sungsuchung</font>

38
00:04:38,620 --> 00:04:42,517
<font color="yellow">Ratu Suri sangat terkejut.</font>

39
00:04:42,517 --> 00:04:46,975
<font color="yellow">Beliau mengirimimu pengawal agar energimu tidak berkurang.</font>

40
00:04:46,975 --> 00:04:49,406
<font color="yellow">Jangan khawatirkan apapun</font>

41
00:04:49,406 --> 00:04:53,190
<font color="yellow">dan lanjutkan persiapan upacaranya.</font>

42
00:04:57,793 --> 00:05:02,773
<font color="yellow">Betapa pedulinya dia padaku di saat dia naik takhta sekarang.</font>

43
00:05:02,773 --> 00:05:05,019
<font color="yellow">Aku sangat paham.</font>

44
00:05:05,019 --> 00:05:08,071
<font color="yellow">Tolong sampaikan terima kasihku pada Ratu Suri.</font>

45
00:05:15,290 --> 00:05:17,838
<font color="yellow"><i>Dia berterima kasih padaku?</i></font>

46
00:05:20,141 --> 00:05:22,230
<font color="yellow">Jalang jahat itu.</font>

47
00:05:24,502 --> 00:05:27,841
<font color="yellow">Perhatikan dari dekat apa yang dilakukan Hong Joo</font>

48
00:05:27,841 --> 00:05:30,560
<font color="yellow">dan suruh mereka laporkan semua tentang Baginda padaku.</font>

49
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:32,040
<font color="yellow">Ya, Yang Mulia.</font>

50
00:05:44,456 --> 00:05:48,264
<font color="yellow">Mereka pasti punya hubungan persaudaraan yang sangat spesial.</font>

51
00:05:56,983 --> 00:06:00,406
<font color="yellow">Aku tak tahu kita akan bertemu lagi seperti ini.</font>

52
00:06:00,406 --> 00:06:02,603
<font color="yellow">Bagaimana bisa kau ke sini?</font>

53
00:06:04,983 --> 00:06:06,529
<font color="yellow">Itu...</font>

54
00:06:07,190 --> 00:06:08,254
<font color="yellow">Mungkinkah...</font>

55
00:06:11,238 --> 00:06:13,086
<font color="yellow">Karena dia?</font>

56
00:06:18,009 --> 00:06:21,791
<font color="yellow">Bukan. Ada yang harus kuurus.</font>

57
00:06:23,471 --> 00:06:26,660
<font color="yellow">Ayah...</font>

58
00:06:26,660 --> 00:06:29,365
<font color="yellow">sehat-sehat saja, kan?</font>

59
00:06:37,259 --> 00:06:39,362
<font color="yellow">Gara-gara aku...</font>

60
00:06:40,343 --> 00:06:42,988
<font color="yellow">Apa sesuatu terjadi hari itu?</font>

61
00:06:48,134 --> 00:06:50,059
<font color="yellow">Yeon Hui.</font>

62
00:06:50,059 --> 00:06:54,857
<font color="yellow">Kita bisa bicarakan lagi ini. Kita bisa bertemu besok</font>

63
00:06:54,857 --> 00:06:57,281
<font color="yellow">lusa, dan tulat (sesudah lusa).</font>

64
00:06:57,281 --> 00:07:00,677
<font color="yellow">Semuanya. Sekaligus. Hm?</font>

65
00:07:15,180 --> 00:07:18,992
<font color="yellow">- Kami dari tadi mencarimu, Tuan.
- Ada apa?</font>

66
00:07:18,992 --> 00:07:21,630
<font color="yellow">Sejak kemarin, Baginda Raja mencari Tuan.</font>

67
00:07:27,309 --> 00:07:30,670
<font color="yellow">Yeon Hui. Besok kita bertemu lagi di sini.</font>

68
00:07:42,202 --> 00:07:45,502
<font color="yellow">Saat kita bertemu lagi, akan kutanyakan kejahatanmu.</font>

69
00:07:45,502 --> 00:07:48,632
<font color="yellow">Aku tak pernah lakukan kejahatan.</font>

70
00:07:56,305 --> 00:07:58,519
<font color="yellow"><i>Poong Yeon.</i></font>

71
00:07:58,519 --> 00:08:03,175
<font color="yellow">Aku terisolasi dan tertahan. Hanya kau yang bisa kupercaya.</font>

72
00:08:03,175 --> 00:08:05,939
<font color="yellow">Ada yang harus kau lakukan.</font>

73
00:08:06,742 --> 00:08:08,634
<font color="yellow">Silakan lanjutkan.</font>

74
00:08:10,228 --> 00:08:13,228
<font color="yellow">Kudengar Ratu Suri melahirkan putri yang terkutuk.</font>

75
00:08:13,228 --> 00:08:16,247
<font color="yellow">Sepertinya putri itulah penyebab penyakitku.</font>

76
00:08:16,247 --> 00:08:19,802
<font color="yellow">Kuharus temukan dia agar penyakitku sembuh</font>

77
00:08:19,802 --> 00:08:22,065
<font color="yellow">dan mengambil alih kuasaku dari Ratu Suri.</font>

78
00:08:22,065 --> 00:08:26,379
<font color="yellow">- Apa itu yang Hong Joo katakan?
- Ada apa?</font>

79
00:08:26,379 --> 00:08:29,262
<font color="yellow">Apa aku tampak menyedihkan bagimu? Mendengarkan ucapan dukun belaka?</font>

80
00:08:30,209 --> 00:08:31,420
<font color="yellow">Yang Mulia.</font>

81
00:08:31,420 --> 00:08:33,591
<font color="yellow">Karena Yang Mulia menderita akibat penyakit ini</font>

82
00:08:33,591 --> 00:08:36,057
<font color="yellow">sepertinya Yang Mulia dibutakan oleh ucapan plin-plan seorang dukun.</font>

83
00:08:36,057 --> 00:08:38,582
<font color="yellow">Kudengar ayahmu menyelamatkan</font>

84
00:08:38,582 --> 00:08:41,486
<font color="yellow">putri yang seharusnya dibunuh.</font>

85
00:08:44,320 --> 00:08:48,696
<font color="yellow">Ketua Dukun memanfaatkan penyakitku dan mengambil alih Sungsuchung.</font>

86
00:08:48,696 --> 00:08:50,456
<font color="yellow">Dan...</font>

87
00:08:50,456 --> 00:08:53,366
<font color="yellow">ayahmu telah memanipulasi Ratu Suri agar</font>

88
00:08:53,366 --> 00:08:55,662
<font color="yellow">membangung kembali Cabang Taoist Kerajaan.</font>

89
00:08:58,123 --> 00:09:00,691
<font color="yellow">Ayahku sudah kembali?</font>

90
00:09:02,206 --> 00:09:05,235
<font color="yellow">Pasti ada sebab kenapa mereka tiba-tiba kembali ke istana.</font>

91
00:09:05,235 --> 00:09:09,710
<font color="yellow">Pasti karena putri itu.</font>

92
00:09:13,006 --> 00:09:14,179
<font color="yellow">Poong Yeon.</font>

93
00:09:15,681 --> 00:09:20,620
<font color="yellow">Jika hidupku dalam bahaya, kau akan lakukan apa?</font>

94
00:09:21,892 --> 00:09:25,139
<font color="yellow">Akan kukorbankan hidupku demi Yang Mulia.</font>

95
00:09:26,065 --> 00:09:27,495
<font color="yellow">Tentu.</font>

96
00:09:28,389 --> 00:09:31,595
<font color="yellow">Kalau begitu...</font>

97
00:09:31,595 --> 00:09:34,825
<font color="yellow">bisa kau putuskan hubungan dengan ayahmu demi aku?</font>

98
00:09:36,246 --> 00:09:38,961
<font color="yellow">Aku harus tahu apa bisa kupercaya dukun itu</font>

99
00:09:38,961 --> 00:09:41,725
<font color="yellow">dan apakah putri masih hidup atau tidak.</font>

100
00:09:41,725 --> 00:09:43,539
<font color="yellow">Itu sebabnya</font>

101
00:09:43,539 --> 00:09:47,190
<font color="yellow">jangan gunakan perasaan pribadimu</font>

102
00:09:47,190 --> 00:09:49,139
<font color="yellow">dan demi kebaikan negeri ini dan aku</font>

103
00:09:49,139 --> 00:09:51,793
<font color="yellow">investigasi ayahmu.</font>

104
00:09:51,793 --> 00:09:54,416
<font color="yellow">Jika ucapan dukun itu benar</font>

105
00:09:54,416 --> 00:09:57,940
<font color="yellow">kau harus temukan putri itu dan bawa dia diam-diam padaku.</font>

106
00:10:08,572 --> 00:10:12,708
<font color="yellow">Oh ya, tidakkah kau merasa sedikit gagal?</font>

107
00:10:12,708 --> 00:10:16,061
<font color="yellow">Kupikir aku bakal bertemu Jubah Tuan Merah.</font>

108
00:10:16,061 --> 00:10:19,823
<font color="yellow">Sepertinya dia mungkin dia langsung melarikan diri dari kita.</font>

109
00:10:19,823 --> 00:10:21,693
<font color="yellow">Mungkin.</font>

110
00:10:21,693 --> 00:10:24,514
<font color="yellow">Kupikir aku bakal bertarung dengannya hari ini.</font>

111
00:10:24,514 --> 00:10:26,778
<font color="yellow">Sepertinya dia beruntung.</font>

112
00:10:29,056 --> 00:10:31,695
<font color="yellow">Suara apa tadi? Ayo, Kak. Ayo cek!</font>

113
00:10:31,695 --> 00:10:34,381
<font color="yellow">Dia dituntut karena telah memperolok bangsawan.</font>

114
00:10:34,381 --> 00:10:36,351
<font color="yellow">Minggir!</font>

115
00:10:38,562 --> 00:10:39,923
<font color="yellow">Lepaskan aku!</font>

116
00:10:42,119 --> 00:10:45,392
<font color="yellow">- Memperolok bangsawan...
- Kenapa mereka begitu padanya?</font>

117
00:10:45,392 --> 00:10:47,094
<font color="yellow">Penghinaan di hadapan umum.</font>

118
00:10:47,094 --> 00:10:49,258
<font color="yellow">Dengan meyeret penjahatnya</font>

119
00:10:49,258 --> 00:10:53,961
<font color="yellow">mereka umumkan kejahatannya pada publik dan mempermalukannya.</font>

120
00:10:58,714 --> 00:11:01,105
<font color="yellow">Tuan... Seo Ri...</font>

121
00:11:02,179 --> 00:11:05,125
<font color="yellow"><i>[Akibat Memperolok Bangsawan]</i>
Lepaskan aku.</font>

122
00:11:05,125 --> 00:11:07,787
<font color="yellow">Aku tidak salah! Lepaskan aku!</font>

123
00:11:07,787 --> 00:11:10,325
<font color="yellow">Dia masih belum sadar.</font>

124
00:11:13,470 --> 00:11:14,985
<font color="yellow">Semua sudah lihat, kan?</font>

125
00:11:14,985 --> 00:11:19,979
<font color="yellow">Dia menghina sistem hierarkis dengan meremehkan bangsawan.</font>

126
00:11:19,979 --> 00:11:23,711
<font color="yellow">Akan kuseret dia ke sekitar kota sampai dia menyadari kesalahannya</font>

127
00:11:23,711 --> 00:11:25,662
<font color="yellow">dan kuikat dia di pohon ini.</font>

128
00:11:25,662 --> 00:11:28,746
<font color="yellow">Kalian semua sebaiknya perhatikan dia baik-baik</font>

129
00:11:28,746 --> 00:11:30,991
<font color="yellow">dan setialah pada hukum. Paham?</font>

130
00:11:31,611 --> 00:11:34,383
<font color="yellow">Dasar bajingan sialan!</font>

131
00:11:34,383 --> 00:11:39,307
<font color="yellow">Lepaskan aku sebelum kupotong ususmu dengan sendok.</font>

132
00:11:39,307 --> 00:11:41,865
<font color="yellow">- Lepaskan aku!
- Jalang ini!</font>

133
00:11:41,865 --> 00:11:44,068
<font color="yellow">Kau sungguh merasa Heo Joon akan datang?</font>

134
00:11:44,068 --> 00:11:48,417
<font color="yellow">Tidak akan. Kami tak ada hubungan. Untuk apa dia datang menyelamatkanku?</font>

135
00:11:48,417 --> 00:11:52,407
<font color="yellow">Kalau kau mencoba membujuknya, pilih umpan yang tepat! Dasar bodoh.</font>

136
00:11:54,388 --> 00:11:56,721
<font color="yellow">Kalian semua lihat, kan?</font>

137
00:11:56,721 --> 00:12:00,322
<font color="yellow">Dia melakukan kejahatan! Menghina bangsawan!</font>

138
00:12:01,899 --> 00:12:07,097
<font color="yellow">Bisa saja kubunuh kau di sini sekarang.</font>

139
00:12:07,097 --> 00:12:11,755
<font color="yellow">Dari tadi aku sudah menahannya.</font>

140
00:12:11,755 --> 00:12:16,447
<font color="yellow">Tapi entah berapa lama lagi kesabaranku bisa bertahan.</font>

141
00:12:16,447 --> 00:12:20,355
<font color="yellow">Apa dia sebabkan masalah ini untuk menangkapmu?</font>

142
00:12:20,714 --> 00:12:22,326
<font color="yellow">Ayo.</font>

143
00:12:22,326 --> 00:12:25,912
<font color="yellow"><i>Kenapa kelas rendahan tak tahu tempatnya?</i></font>

144
00:12:25,912 --> 00:12:30,160
<font color="yellow"><i>Mereka hanya sadar saat orang tuanya dihukum.</i></font>

145
00:12:30,160 --> 00:12:32,192
<font color="yellow"><i>Mana ibumu?</i></font>

146
00:12:34,581 --> 00:12:36,946
<font color="yellow">Tuan! Tuan! Tuan...</font>

147
00:12:58,662 --> 00:13:00,981
<font color="yellow">Mereka mendatangimu tanpa tahu tempatnya.</font>

148
00:13:04,374 --> 00:13:07,818
<font color="yellow">- Kau bisa lari?
- Tentu bisa. Sangat cepat.</font>

149
00:13:08,965 --> 00:13:10,749
<font color="yellow">Bersiap-siaplah, Seo Ri.</font>

150
00:13:26,190 --> 00:13:28,332
<font color="yellow">Apa-apaan ini? Astaga. Dasar bodoh.</font>

151
00:13:42,298 --> 00:13:44,924
<font color="yellow">Membahayakan. Apa yang kau lakukan?</font>

152
00:13:44,924 --> 00:13:47,980
<font color="yellow">Bahkan jika dia membuatmu murka...</font>

153
00:13:49,073 --> 00:13:50,956
<font color="yellow">Aku belum selesai.</font>

154
00:14:07,717 --> 00:14:10,042
<font color="yellow">Ke mana dia? Cepat sekali...</font>

155
00:14:35,576 --> 00:14:38,666
<font color="yellow">Jangan lihat. Tetaplah di sana.</font>

156
00:14:57,283 --> 00:15:00,903
<font color="yellow">Aku harus apa agar kau berhenti?</font>

157
00:15:00,903 --> 00:15:02,879
<font color="yellow">Berhenti?</font>

158
00:15:04,303 --> 00:15:07,256
<font color="yellow">Aku akan berhenti jika kau mati.</font>

159
00:15:07,256 --> 00:15:08,711
<font color="yellow">Hei.</font>

160
00:15:08,711 --> 00:15:13,369
<font color="yellow">Pernah kau memikirkan apa yang sudah kulalui?</font>

161
00:15:13,369 --> 00:15:18,057
<font color="yellow">Andai kau tak lancang, aku takkan dibanding-bandingkan denganmu.</font>

162
00:15:18,057 --> 00:15:22,214
<font color="yellow">Ibuku juga takkan memperlakukanku seperti orang bodph yang tak punya kemampuan.</font>

163
00:15:22,214 --> 00:15:26,875
<font color="yellow">Tanpamu, aku juga takkan jadi begini!</font>

164
00:15:27,941 --> 00:15:31,312
<font color="yellow">Karena itukah kau bunuh ibuku?</font>

165
00:15:31,312 --> 00:15:34,129
<font color="yellow">- Karena tak suka aku?
- Siapa?</font>

166
00:15:34,129 --> 00:15:36,976
<font color="yellow">Hm? Aku?</font>

167
00:15:36,976 --> 00:15:39,538
<font color="yellow">Aku tak membunuhnya.</font>

168
00:15:39,538 --> 00:15:43,216
<font color="yellow">Ibumu sendiri yang merangkak ke dalam api.</font>

169
00:15:43,216 --> 00:15:45,090
<font color="yellow">Hei. Pikirkanlah.</font>

170
00:15:45,090 --> 00:15:48,993
<font color="yellow">Bagaimana bisa pelayan yang sudah melarikan diri dibolehkan hidup?</font>

171
00:15:48,993 --> 00:15:51,586
<font color="yellow">Kaulah yang menyeret ibumu ke dalam api itu.</font>

172
00:15:51,586 --> 00:15:53,360
<font color="yellow">Kau.</font>

173
00:16:02,648 --> 00:16:04,519
<font color="yellow">Baiklah.</font>

174
00:16:06,206 --> 00:16:07,991
<font color="yellow">Kau benar.</font>

175
00:16:09,981 --> 00:16:12,860
<font color="yellow">Gara-gara aku...</font>

176
00:16:14,292 --> 00:16:17,417
<font color="yellow">Karena aku tak punya kekuatan</font>

177
00:16:17,417 --> 00:16:19,893
<font color="yellow">tak bisa kulindungi ibuku.</font>

178
00:16:20,966 --> 00:16:25,335
<font color="yellow">Pada akhirnya, satu-satunya cara agar kauu tak halangi jalanku...</font>

179
00:16:27,605 --> 00:16:29,852
<font color="yellow">dengan ini.</font>

180
00:16:32,096 --> 00:16:33,927
